		<td colspan="7" vAlign="top" class="content">While the Fire District has determined optimal staffing levels for its respective fire stations and specialty teams; there is, from time to time, a need for additional volunteers.  To be a member and active volunteer participant of the Boone County Fire Protection District or Missouri Task Force 1 is to be held in very high regard in our community.  The organization has established an extremely high level of respect and professionalism and it holds its commitment to the community in the highest order.  
