		<td colspan="7" vAlign="top" class="content">Should you desire to volunteer as one of the Boone County&#146;s finest and should you be accepted, you would find yourself as a member of a very noble breed of men and women who have found themselves bound together by a strong determination and commitment to their fellow man.  This is indeed a very tight family, which is bound together by a very important mission and is asked to perform in an arena that is very demanding and challenging.  If you believe you have what it takes to contribute to and be a part of this most important endeavor, please review the remainder of our website and contact us for additional membership information.
